sequenceDiagram
  participant CLI as CLI
  participant Runtime as Runtime
  participant Provider as Provider Adapter
  participant API as Model API

  CLI->>Runtime: user input
  Runtime->>Runtime: build ChatRequest
  Runtime->>Provider: stream(ChatRequest)
  Provider->>API: provider-specific streaming request
  API-->>Provider: raw stream events
  Provider-->>Runtime: message_start
  Provider-->>Runtime: text_delta
  Runtime-->>CLI: print delta
  Provider-->>Runtime: usage / message_stop
  Runtime-->>Runtime: record turn result
  Runtime-->>CLI: finish prompt
